description: Keep your most important items secure and organized. The SD Pixel Pocket Rocket keeps those small but invaluable SD memory cards safely stored in one place. No more lost SD cards, and no more found SD cards in the bottom of the washing machine. Additionally, it can be tethered to your bag, clothing, briefcase, backpack, etc. for additional security with the quick clip lanyard. You buy a holster for your camera and a filter for your lens; so why not organize and protect the most important part of the puzzle? Compact carrier for 9 SD memory cards Clear pockets make identification easy Folds flat when not in use, easily stored Business card slot and removable lanyard with quick clips Technical Specifications: 4.5" L x 2.5" W x .5" H (11.5  6.5  1.5 cm) 0.1lbs (0.04kg)
title: Think Tank SD Pixel Pocket Rocket, Holds 9 SD Memory Cards
